reviewText: This is an excellent movie set, love everything about it.
I am disappointed that Deja Vu is not playable due to it's region but I knew that prior to purchasing.  What a great collection of movies!!!

Action/drama movies are a dime a dozen! Few have the originality and strong story line to captivate such as these. So many phenomenal actors: Washington, Hackman, Smith, Connery, Cage, Affleck, Willis and more all rolled into one!
